            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "\r\nBefore (lua5.1, luajit)\r\n```\r\n~/b/neovim master ❯ VIMRUNTIME=runtime build/bin/nvim --clean +'=debug.getinfo(vim.fn.maparg(\"]<Space>\", \"n\", 0, 1).callback, \"Sl\")' --headless +q\r\n{\r\n  currentline = -1,\r\n  lastlinedefined = 0,\r\n  linedefined = 0,\r\n  short_src = \"vim/_core/defaults.lua\",\r\n  source = \"@vim/_core/defaults.lua\",\r\n  what = \"Lua\"\r\n}\r\n~/b/neovim master ❯ VIMRUNTIME=runtime build/bin/nvim --clean +'=debug.getinfo(vim.fn.maparg(\"]<Space>\", \"n\", 0, 1).callback, \"Sl\")' --headless +q\r\n{\r\n  currentline = -1,\r\n  lastlinedefined = 456,\r\n  linedefined = 452,\r\n  short_src = \"?\",\r\n  source = \"=?\",\r\n  what = \"Lua\"\r\n}⏎\r\n```\r\n\r\nAfter (maybe a bad example here since zig build is not byte compiled previously, so it always have correct debug info before/after, but cmake build output would also be looks like this):\r\n```\r\n~/b/neovim precompile2 ❯ zig build\r\n~/b/neovim precompile2 ❯ VIMRUNTIME=runtime zig-out/bin/nvim --clean +'=debug.getinfo(vim.fn.maparg(\"]<Space>\", \"n\", 0, 1).callback, \"Sl\")' --headless +q\r\n{\r\n  currentline = -1,\r\n  lastlinedefined = 456,\r\n  linedefined = 452,\r\n  short_src = \"/home/phan/b/neovim/runtime/lua/vim/_core/defaults.lua\",\r\n  source = \"@/home/phan/b/neovim/runtime/lua/vim/_core/defaults.lua\",\r\n  what = \"Lua\"\r\n}⏎\r\n```\r\n",
